summary: ...JERRY EXPECTED TO BE NEAR THE NORTHERN LEEWARD ISLANDS THIS EVENING AND TONIGHT... ...TROPICAL STORM WARNING ISSUED FOR PORTIONS OF THE NORTHERN LEEWARD ISLANDS... As of 2:00 PM AST Thu Oct 09 the center of Jerry was located near 16.5, -60.0 with movement WNW at 18 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1000 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
